{"id": 1344, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年，你花过什么冤枉钱？", "description": "弄了一个娇气的发型，冲动消费买了不常用的东西……感觉辛辛苦苦攒的钱都用来拉动GDP了。（题图来自：Hanna Barczyk）", "record_count": 2754, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161124105631KpGCfMq94SbY1NaT.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-25T03:00:50Z", "options": [{"id": 136704, "content": "PSV单机被虐 心碎", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 99741}, {"id": 136960, "content": "买了个小垃圾桶打算办公室里用，但事实证明，我的强迫症让我没办法忍受垃圾桶里有东西存在。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829995}, {"id": 137472, "content": "为暖暖女儿买了很多衣服，但是换了手机把暖暖卸载了……………", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 848553}, {"id": 140544, "content": "买了几双假鞋，妈蛋……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 857944}, {"id": 136705, "content": "物价太高…花着花着就没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 845953}, {"id": 136961, "content": "第一次用携程买火车票，卡了，以为没买成功。过了好几天才发现买成功了，然而已经搭火车去了别的地方? 然后买了台湾机票，办入台证的时候发现签注是团签?mission removed", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665380}, {"id": 136706, "content": "老板说我平头好看，推平了头，188。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 396158}, {"id": 136962, "content": "买了一堆同款商品，只因为打折", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685842}, {"id": 136707, "content": "买了法拉利?", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207599}, {"id": 136963, "content": "说得好像自己有钱一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126700}, {"id": 136708, "content": "我根本没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 845957}, {"id": 136964, "content": "网恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781892}, {"id": 136709, "content": "刚刚看了下支付宝十一月账单，原来我这么有钱??", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198262}, {"id": 136965, "content": "双手已剁", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846748}, {"id": 136710, "content": "买了java书，发现自己不喜欢撸代码", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766922}, {"id": 136966, "content": "刚买的s7一个月丢了，又买了7，看牙本来四千可以，结果花了近一万还不好，其中路费2000多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846755}, {"id": 136711, "content": "买了水卡，然后丢了。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843295}, {"id": 136967, "content": "隐形眼镜非常不舒服！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747562}, {"id": 136712, "content": "钱本来就不多，然后节约的额度小了一点，就没钱了，冤枉死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790444}, {"id": 136968, "content": "买了二张机票，领导不同意假期，没法退。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846769}, {"id": 136713, "content": "steam垃圾平台，耗我钱财", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835165}, {"id": 136969, "content": "十一国庆在实体店买的衣服到了双十一旗舰店便宜了700多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846770}, {"id": 137225, "content": "双十一买的一切。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449117}, {"id": 136714, "content": "强迫症发作算作死还是冤枉呢...", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192542}, {"id": 137994, "content": "啊啊啊啊啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851311}, {"id": 136715, "content": "掏宝  当当  京东 就是一个买", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273034}, {"id": 136971, "content": "买了好几双鞋子", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 845635}, {"id": 137483, "content": "不应该是四级资料吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 80249}, {"id": 136716, "content": "淘宝 京东 当当就是一个买。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273034}, {"id": 136717, "content": "花几千块充值游戏，结果发现是大坑，果断退游！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776954}, {"id": 136462, "content": "本来想等到圣诞节开始日淘屯东西，结果汇率高到没眼看", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 136718, "content": "剑侠情缘手游元宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479074}, {"id": 137486, "content": "现在的感觉就是 现在有钱 一会就没了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 848554}, {"id": 137742, "content": "办了卡，又把卡丢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849669}, {"id": 151822, "content": "炉石传说的388", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896826}, {"id": 136463, "content": "烫了一个浅色头发，每个月补颜色的钱加起来可以又烫好几个头", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 136719, "content": "氪……", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372889}, {"id": 137743, "content": "办了卡，又把卡丢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849669}, {"id": 136464, "content": "跟风买了洗眼水，结果三个月保质期快过了也没洗几回", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 136720, "content": "买了只阿拉斯加没几天细小病毒死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 825454}, {"id": 136721, "content": "买了只阿拉斯加没几天细小病毒死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 825454}, {"id": 142353, "content": "网球拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 62504}, {"id": 143889, "content": "为她花的每一分", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867018}, {"id": 136722, "content": "信用卡被朋友的哥哥偷去盗刷，结果8KRMB没要回来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836711}, {"id": 136723, "content": "各种非必需打车